== 製作 ==
《-{光榮擂台}-》於2013年12月在[[巴拿馬|巴拿馬]]開拍<ref>{{cite news|title=Usher shows off afro, fit physique as Sugar Ray Leonard in newly released photos from ‘Hands of Stone’ film|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/usher-shows-afro-fit-physique-sugar-ray-leonard-hands-stone-article-1.1534848|accessdate=6 December 2013|newspaper=nydailynews.com|date=2 December 2013|archive-date=2016-03-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313084140/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv-movies/usher-shows-afro-fit-physique-sugar-ray-leonard-hands-stone-article-1.1534848|dead-url=no}}</ref>，於2014年3月結束。

== 發行 ==
[[File:Cannes_2016_26.jpg|thumb]]上]]
2015年5月，[[溫斯坦影業|溫斯坦影業]]獲得了電影的美國發行權，並打算於兩千間戲院放映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/robert-de-niro-boxing-movie-hands-of-stone-bought-weinstein-1201495878/|title=Cannes: Robert De Niro Boxing Movie ‘Hands of Stone’ Bought by Weinstein Co.|publisher=Variety.com|first=Maane|last=Khatachatourian|date=May 14, 2015|accessdate=February 23, 2016|archive-date=2016-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160504145834/http://variety.com/2015/film/news/robert-de-niro-boxing-movie-hands-of-stone-bought-weinstein-1201495878/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影定於2016年8月26日在美國的八百間戲院上映，8月31日前，戲院擴增至兩千五百間<ref name="#1"/><ref name=preview/>。

== 反響 ==
=== 評價 ===
《-{光榮擂台}-》獲得的評價褒貶不一。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]根據82條評論而持有44%的新鮮度，平均得分5.3／10；該網站共識：「《-{光榮擂台}-》的強力演員和引人入勝的真實生活故事都還不足以彌補其擁擠的敘事和公式化的劇本」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hands_of_stone/ |title=Hands of Stone (2016) |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=September 13, 2016 |archive-date=2016-10-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011052144/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/hands_of_stone/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分55，評價兩極<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/hands-of-stone|title=Hands of Stone reviews|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=September 4, 2016|archive-date=2016-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107220915/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/hands-of-stone|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

根據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間約落在「A+」<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/08/dont-breathe-suicide-squad-southside-with-you-mechanic-insurrection-box-office-1201809180/amp/ |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-11-05 |archive-date=2016-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161009171924/http://deadline.com/2016/08/dont-breathe-suicide-squad-southside-with-you-mechanic-insurrection-box-office-1201809180/amp/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。觀眾的反應比影評人好上許多。

=== 票房 ===
電影在北美於2016年8月26日上映，估計在首週末能從八百一十間戲院中獲得200萬至300萬美元的票房<ref name="preview">{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/08/dont-breathe-suicide-squad-mechanic-resurrection-southside-with-you-hands-of-stone-1201808025/ |title=‘Don’t Breathe’ Could Suffocate ‘Suicide Squad’ During Sluggish Summer Weekend: Box Office Preview |work=deadline.com |accessdate=2016-11-05 |archive-date=2016-08-25 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20160825120030/http://deadline.com/2016/08/dont-breathe-suicide-squad-mechanic-resurrection-southside-with-you-hands-of-stone-1201808025/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在有限戲院放映的情況下，電影於首週末獲得170萬美元的票房，位居當週第十六<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/08/dont-breathe-suicide-squad-southside-with-you-mechanic-insurrection-box-office-1201809180/|title=‘Don’t Breathe’ Screams $26M+ Opening, Gives Sony 3rd Summer Cash Cow After ‘Sausage Party’, ‘Shallows’: Early Sunday Update|author=Anthony D'Alessandro|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|accessdate=August 28, 2016|archive-date=2019-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191210230212/https://deadline.com/2016/08/dont-breathe-suicide-squad-southside-with-you-mechanic-insurrection-box-office-1201809180/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。第二個週末，儘管放映的戲院增加至一千兩百零一間，但當週票房僅130萬美元，位居當週第二十<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2016/09/dont-breathe-light-between-oceans-morgan-labor-day-weekend-box-office-1201812978/ |title=he’ Still Has Oxygen, ‘Suicide Squad’ Seizes $300M+, ‘Morgan’ D.O.A. : Labor Day Weekend B.O. |work=deadline.com |accessdate=2016-11-05 |archive-date=2016-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161104233025/http://deadline.com/2016/09/dont-breathe-light-between-oceans-morgan-labor-day-weekend-box-office-1201812978/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

